67 std::vector <std::vector<double>> getTraverseInputData(Local<Object> obj) {
68  auto const & arrayTmp = obj->Get(Nan::New<String>("traverseData").ToLocalChecked());
69  auto const & array = v8::Local<v8::Array>::Cast(arrayTmp);
70 
71  std::vector<std::vector <double> > traverseData(array->Length());
72  for (std::size_t i = 0; i < array->Length(); i++) {
73  auto const & innerArray = v8::Local<v8::Array>::Cast(array->Get(i)->ToObject());
74  traverseData.at(i).resize(innerArray->Length());
75  for (std::size_t j = 0; j < innerArray->Length(); j++) {
76  traverseData.at(i).at(j) = innerArray->Get(j)->NumberValue();
77  }
78  }
79 
80  return traverseData;
81 }

106 PlaneData getPlaneData() {
107  auto planeDataV8 = inp->ToObject()->Get(Nan::New<String>("PlaneData").ToLocalChecked())->ToObject();
108 
109  auto const addlTravTmp = planeDataV8->Get(Nan::New<String>("AddlTraversePlanes").ToLocalChecked());
110  auto const & addlTravArray = v8::Local<v8::Array>::Cast(addlTravTmp);
111  std::vector<TraversePlane> addlTravPlanes;
112 
113  for (std::size_t i = 0; i < addlTravArray->Length(); i++) {
114  addlTravPlanes.emplace_back(constructTraverse(addlTravArray->Get(i)->ToObject()));
115  }
116 
117  return {
118  constructFlange(planeDataV8->Get(Nan::New<String>("FanInletFlange").ToLocalChecked())->ToObject()),
119  constructFlange(planeDataV8->Get(Nan::New<String>("FanEvaseOrOutletFlange").ToLocalChecked())->ToObject()),
120  constructTraverse(planeDataV8->Get(Nan::New<String>("FlowTraverse").ToLocalChecked())->ToObject()),
121  std::move(addlTravPlanes),
122  constructMst(planeDataV8->Get(Nan::New<String>("InletMstPlane").ToLocalChecked())->ToObject()),
123  constructMst(planeDataV8->Get(Nan::New<String>("OutletMstPlane").ToLocalChecked())->ToObject()),
124  Get("totalPressureLossBtwnPlanes1and4", planeDataV8),
125  Get("totalPressureLossBtwnPlanes2and5", planeDataV8),
126  GetBool("plane5upstreamOfPlane2", planeDataV8)
127  };

422 NAN_METHOD(getPlaneResults) {
423  Local<Object> rv = Nan::New<Object>();
424  inp = info[0]->ToObject();
425 
426  try {
427  auto planeData = getPlaneData();
428  auto baseGasDensity = getBaseGasDensity();
429  auto const output = PlaneData::NodeBinding::calculate(planeData, baseGasDensity);
430  Handle<Array> addlTravPlanes = Array::New(v8::Isolate::GetCurrent(), output.addlTravPlanes.size());
431  std::size_t index = 0;
432 
433  auto const setData = [&rv, &addlTravPlanes, &index](const PlaneData::NodeBinding::Data & data, std::string const & name,
434  bool isArray = false, bool isStaticPressure = false, const double staticPressure = 0) {
435  r = Nan::New<Object>();
436  SetR("gasDensity", data.gasDensity);
437  SetR("gasVolumeFlowRate", data.gasVolumeFlowRate);
438  SetR("gasVelocity", data.gasVelocity);
439  SetR("gasVelocityPressure", data.gasVelocityPressure);
440  SetR("gasTotalPressure", data.gasTotalPressure);
441  if (isStaticPressure) {
442  SetR("staticPressure", staticPressure);
443  }
444 
445  if (isArray) {
446  addlTravPlanes->Set(index, r);
447  } else {
448  Nan::Set(rv, Nan::New<String>(name).ToLocalChecked(), r);
449  }
450  };
451 
452  for (auto const & data : output.addlTravPlanes) {
453  setData(data, "", true);
454  index++;
455  }
456  Nan::Set(rv, Nan::New<String>("AddlTraversePlanes").ToLocalChecked(), addlTravPlanes);
457 
458  setData(output.fanInletFlange, "FanInletFlange", false, true, output.fanInletFlange.staticPressure);
459  setData(output.fanOrEvaseOutletFlange, "FanOrEvaseOutletFlange", false, true, output.fanOrEvaseOutletFlange.staticPressure);
460  setData(output.flowTraverse, "FlowTraverse");
461  setData(output.inletMstPlane, "InletMstPlane");
462  setData(output.outletMstPlane, "OutletMstPlane");
463  } catch (std::runtime_error const & e) {
464  std::string const what = e.what();
465  ThrowError(std::string("std::runtime_error thrown in getPlaneResults - fan.h: " + what).c_str());
466  }
467 
468  info.GetReturnValue().Set(rv);
469 }

512 FanCurveData getFanBaseCurveData() {
513 
514  auto const & arrayTmp = inp->ToObject()->Get(Nan::New<String>("BaseCurveData").ToLocalChecked());
515  auto const & array = v8::Local<v8::Array>::Cast(arrayTmp);

564 void returnResultData(std::vector<ResultData> const & results) {
565  std::size_t index = 0;
566  Handle<Array> outerArray = Array::New(v8::Isolate::GetCurrent(), results.size());
567  for (auto const & row : results) {
568  Handle<Array> array = Array::New(v8::Isolate::GetCurrent(), 4);
569  array->Set(0, Nan::New<Number>(row.flow));
570  array->Set(1, Nan::New<Number>(row.pressure));
571  array->Set(2, Nan::New<Number>(row.power));
572  array->Set(3, Nan::New<Number>(row.efficiency));
573  outerArray->Set(index, array);
574  index++;
575  }
576  Nan::Set(r, Nan::New<String>("ResultData").ToLocalChecked(), outerArray);
577 }
